name: CVE-2025-55184
description: React Server Components 19.0.0 to 19.2.1 including react-server-dom-parcel, react-server-dom-turbopack, and react-server-dom-webpack contain an insecure deserialization vulnerability caused by unsafe payload deserialization in Server Function endpoints, letting unauthenticated attackers cause denial of service by hanging the server process.
